Steps to Execute-:

1. Unzip file.
2. Import As a Maven Project  in your IDE.
3. Inside src/main/java ->PiglatinApplication.java
4. Right click on PiglatinApplication.java  class and run as JAVA Application.

Testing Steps:-
1. Swagger
 open URL- http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html#!/piglatin-controller/translateInLatinUsingGET
 
And pass your input inside sentence field.

2. Postman
 Call GET api http://localhost:8080/piglatin
 And pass in Params KEY as sentence.
 And value as per your input